  ends?
Example answer: Provided that there are no pending claims, the personal file shall be
  retained for a maximum of 10 years. The retention period commences
  either when the staff member’s employment with the ECB ceases or
  following the last ECB pension payment to the pensioner or their
  entitled dependants. (ECB Staff Rules, page 31)
